LWIP_DBG_TRACE: Flag for LWIP_DEBUGF indicating a tracing message to follow program flow;
LWIP_DBG_STATE: Flag for LWIP_DEBUGF indicating a state debug message to follow module states;
LWIP_DBG_HALT: Flag for LWIP_DEBUGF to halt after printing this debug message</description>
